  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And as the time progressed, we were becoming-- or I was becoming-- more and more aware that more and more people were gone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would see less children than what I played with it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother or father would say, oh the [DUTCH], this and this and this went yesterday, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] without having to say anymore, 'went' meant they're not there anymore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In their house or whatever, anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became, as the time progressed, more and more aware that people were not there anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't really want to use the word 'disappearing.' They were-- yes, they were disappearing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were not there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So as the time progressed, I became more and more aware that [SIGHS] we were different.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you think that's going to happen to you, too?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't really think it was going to happen to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I'd always felt from my mother, because she was English by birth, there would be special consideration given to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were half-English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother, who had one sister, also living in Amsterdam, married to a Dutchman, with a child, my cousin-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she and he survived.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- my mother and she thought we would be somehow interned, or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't think that we would go away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That became more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a lesser possibility when all of a sudden, we were commanded to leave our home where we were.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were forcibly moved to another part of Amsterdam, to what was, in actual fact, a ghetto, one of the parts of Amsterdam which they had proclaimed as a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to leave our home and go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
